---
import BaseLayout from '../../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'ms';
const post = {
  title: 'Pembiayaan Forklift Startup 2026',
  slug: 'pembiayaan-forklift-startup-2026',
  excerpt: 'Forklift untuk gudang dan kilang. 0% deposit. Pinjaman penuh 100%. Tiada had umur. Kelulusan pantas. Untuk perniagaan baharu logistik.',
  date: '2026-01-15',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 5,
  category: 'Pembiayaan Permulaan',
  image: '/images/blog/startup-forklift-financing-2026.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['pembiayaan forklift', 'forklift financing malaysia', '0% deposit', 'pinjaman gudang'],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/ms' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/ms/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/${lang}/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Pembiayaan Permulaan</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('ms-MY', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min baca</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Mulakan Perniagaan Forklift Anda</h2>

      <p>Forklift adalah aset penting dalam gudang dan kilang. Dengan forklift, anda boleh urus barang dengan cepat dan selamat.</p>

      <p>Forklift juga boleh disewakan kepada perniagaan lain. Ini adalah peluang perniagaan yang bagus.</p>

      <p>Tapi beli forklift mahal. RM30,000 untuk forklif 1.5 tan baru. Bank mahu deposit 10-20%. Itu RM3,000 - RM6,000 muka.</p>

      <p>Kami tawarkan 0% deposit. Gunakan duit tu untuk barang lain.</p>

      <h2>Jenis Forklift Untuk Startup</h2>

      <h3>Forklift 1-Ton (Kecil)</h3>
      <p><strong>Harga Baru:</strong> RM25,000 - RM40,000</p>
      <p><strong>Harga Terpakai:</strong> RM8,000 - RM20,000</p>
      <p><strong>Sesuai Untuk:</strong> Gudang kecil, kilang kecil, kedai runcit</p>
      <p><strong>Sewa Bulanan:</strong> RM1,500 - RM2,500</p>

      <h3>Forklift 1.5-2 Tan (Sederhana)</h3>
      <p><strong>Harga Baru:</strong> RM35,000 - RM60,000</p>
      <p><strong>Harga Terpakai:</strong> RM12,000 - RM30,000</p>
      <p><strong>Sesuai Untuk:</strong> Gudang sederhana, kilang, logistik</p>
      <p><strong>Sewa Bulanan:</strong> RM2,000 - RM3,500</p>

      <h3>Forklift 3-5 Tan (Berat)</h3>
      <p><strong>Harga Baru:</strong> RM60,000 - RM100,000</p>
      <p><strong>Harga Terpakai:</strong> RM20,000 - RM50,000</p>
      <p><strong>Sesuai Untuk:</strong> Gudang besar, penghantaran, kontena</p>
      <p><strong>Sewa Bulanan:</strong> RM3,500 - RM6,000</p>

      <h3>Reach Truck (Untuk Rak Tinggi)</h3>
      <p><strong>Harga Baru:</strong> RM50,000 - RM90,000</p>
      <p><strong>Harga Terpakai:</strong> RM15,000 - RM40,000</p>
      <p><strong>Sesuai Untuk:</strong> Gudang bertingkat, lorong kecil</p>
      <p><strong>Sewa Bulanan:</strong> RM3,000 - RM5,500</p>

      <h2>Bank vs Kami</h2>

      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <thead>
          <tr style="background: #2D1810; color: #D4A574;">
            <th style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574; text-align: left;">Item</th>
            <th style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574; text-align: left;">Bank</th>
            <th style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574; text-align: left;">Kami</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Deposit</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">10-20%</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>0%</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background: #F9FAFB;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Pinjaman</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Max 90%</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>100%</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Umur Forklift</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Max 5 tahun</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>Tiada had</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background: #F9FAFB;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Kelulusan</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">4-6 minggu</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>24-48 jam</strong></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Kira Angsuran: Forklift 2-Tan RM30,000</h2>

      <p><strong>Tempoh 4 Tahun:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Angsuran: ~RM750 sebulan</li>
        <li>Sewa: RM2,500 sebulan</li>
        <li>Untung: RM1,750 sebulan</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Tempoh 5 Tahun:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Angsuran: ~RM650 sebulan</li>
        <li>Sewa: RM2,500 sebulan</li>
        <li>Untung: RM1,850 sebulan</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Perniagaan Sewa Forklift</h2>

      <h3>Model Perniagaan 1: Sewa Harian</h3>
      <p>Sewa forklift RM150 sehari. 20 hari kerja = RM3,000 sebulan. Angsuran RM650. Untung RM2,350.</p>

      <h3>Model Perniagaan 2: Sewa Bulanan</h3>
      <p>Sewa forklift RM2,500 sebulan. Angsuran RM650. Untung RM1,850. Pelanggan stabil, income stabil.</p>

      <h3>Model Perniagaan 3: Kontrak Tahunan</h3>
      <p>Sewa RM2,200 sebulan dengan kontrak 1 tahun. Pelanggan dapat diskaun, anda dapat pendapatan stabil.</p>

      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Nak Mulakan Perniagaan Forklift?</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">0% deposit. 100% pinjaman penuh. Forklift baru atau terpakai. Kelulusan 24 jam.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Contact:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Telefon)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
      <CTAButton text="Dapatkan Pembiayaan Sekarang" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h3 {
    color: #8B6F47;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  strong {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  li {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #D4A574;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
